    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >欢迎！</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2162070/extras/8b57c326bec49fe277d66fb78be9c232.poster.avif?t=1706622774\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2162070/extras/8b57c326bec49fe277d66fb78be9c232.webm?t=1706622774\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2162070/extras/8b57c326bec49fe277d66fb78be9c232.mp4?t=1706622774\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>这款游戏，会刷新你对塔防基地建造类游戏的认知！<br>有如狂乱的梦境成真，这便是……《乌利给》！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Ooglian 是什么？</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2162070/extras/81dc9084c9392762f394fd37e2dda0fd.poster.avif?t=1706622774\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2162070/extras/81dc9084c9392762f394fd37e2dda0fd.webm?t=1706622774\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2162070/extras/81dc9084c9392762f394fd37e2dda0fd.mp4?t=1706622774\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>乌利给是个神秘物种。<br>这些小家伙到底是科技盲、还是破坏狂，我们无从知晓，<br>不过它们显然很喜欢将机械砸成破铜烂铁。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >你不是乌利给，</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2162070/extras/6b8c51e499e549720826584b0ad0bca8.poster.avif?t=1706622774\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2162070/extras/6b8c51e499e549720826584b0ad0bca8.webm?t=1706622774\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>你是……你。至于你的具体身份是什么，不好意思，我无权告知。<br>你为什么会出现在这座星球上？<br>你来这里又有什么目的？<br>目前，这些问题的答案都是未知数。或许，保护好你的反应堆，答案自然就会浮出水面。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2162070/extras/b9102a2190eec7fe2e80a272a74abb49.apng?t=1706622774\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2162070/extras/b9102a2190eec7fe2e80a272a74abb49.poster.avif?t=1706622774\" class=\"bb_img\" width=24 height=24 /></picture></span> 围绕反应堆建造基地<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2162070/extras/fdc754751da706185cbc8f1bd48a301b.apng?t=1706622774\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2162070/extras/fdc754751da706185cbc8f1bd48a301b.poster.avif?t=1706622774\" class=\"bb_img\" width=24 height=24 /></picture></span> Ooglian 会被机械吸引过来<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2162070/extras/94449cda041a80a925ed63ab56deaf05.apng?t=1706622774\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2162070/extras/94449cda041a80a925ed63ab56deaf05.poster.avif?t=1706622774\" class=\"bb_img\" width=24 height=24 /></picture></span> Ooglian 试图摧毁你的基地<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2162070/extras/06366c8727c328e12443157e635dc980.apng?t=1706622774\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2162070/extras/06366c8727c328e12443157e635dc980.poster.avif?t=1706622774\" class=\"bb_img\" width=24 height=24 /></picture></span> 建造更多机械来保卫基地<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2162070/extras/94449cda041a80a925ed63ab56deaf05.apng?t=1706622774\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2162070/extras/94449cda041a80a925ed63ab56deaf05.poster.avif?t=1706622774\" class=\"bb_img\" width=24 height=24 /></picture></span> 吸引更多 Ooglian<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2162070/extras/fdc754751da706185cbc8f1bd48a301b.apng?t=1706622774\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2162070/extras/fdc754751da706185cbc8f1bd48a301b.poster.avif?t=1706622774\" class=\"bb_img\" width=24 height=24 /></picture></span> 游戏陷入循环<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2162070/extras/b9102a2190eec7fe2e80a272a74abb49.apng?t=1706622774\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2162070/extras/b9102a2190eec7fe2e80a272a74abb49.poster.avif?t=1706622774\" class=\"bb_img\" width=24 height=24 /></picture></span> <span class=\"bb_strike\">当</span>倘若反应堆被毁，你就会输掉游戏<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2162070/extras/673586455b06fe393a3cbbc7f7ff1243.poster.avif?t=1706622774\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2162070/extras/673586455b06fe393a3cbbc7f7ff1243.webm?t=1706622774\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2162070/extras/673586455b06fe393a3cbbc7f7ff1243.mp4?t=1706622774\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2162070/extras/edc9e3528a373e0feab6c6ae60d2bf57.poster.avif?t=1706622774\" width=198 height=198 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/